parameters: (My stomach... feels heavy... maybe... I'm pregnant...)
(No... don't be dependent. This is... definitely, I'm pregnant...)

I'm pushing myself too hard, aren't I? Trying to be a cute child. I
wonder if that's what they call being devoted. I don't really
understand, but... hehe.

(Just because I'm pushing myself too hard... so what? Get
a grip, me...! He still hasn't come out...!)

Ignoring me again, I wonder. But I'm starting to
understand. Araka, is it the hardest for you when you stay silent?

(I'll give you some breasts, you did a good job practicing, Araka  ...
Oh, could it be that you also want to raise those children?)
"Araka felt a maternal instinct towards it"
I hope the baby is okay, like you, Araka...
"Arakas swollen belly was squeezed and she writhed in agony"
Shall I pat your back? (Your tummy is so squishy.)
"Araka continued to be filled with impurity and became a vessel for expelling impurity"

(Ufufu, my legs are still trembling  Araka, you're such a hardworking
and cute girl )
"In the end, Arakas vagina is loose and cannot hold a child"
Hey, do you think he might be an idiot?

As the colors of the other world grew stronger, Araka anxiously looked
around while observing him. She infused her spiritual power into the
fragments she had picked up.
Ah... ah... ngh, ugh... guh  fu... oh... ugh  gu... ah

The miasma is quite thick... The boundary between the otherworld and
the human world has become significantly thinner.
I thought I could send something that would be helpful to him.
